.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8mt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=5d76d2e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1c5b8a7904a0e0ac39a22e3fdb9b662a917f3136","tid":1582143,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2e080ba7004fdc564156d1c40d2aafa02e5de7a8","tid":1582143,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5b8a7904a0e0ac39a22e3fdb9b662a917f3136","tid":1582143,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e0661926e67a86eb85a01c3fd391bc7bed414401","tid":1582143,"uid":73118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36bf62a485e9aff349a0704c4cfdfc54de57c819","tid":1582143,"uid":266081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">女朋友剛上水出站： (9月20) <br />\n大陸人已到連儂牆視察</span></span><br />\n1000 見到兩個好明顯係大陸鄉里的男人戴耳機，著白衫，望實睇緊上水連儂1的大媽。除左監視，唔會有人企o係天橋路口位，夜晚小販睇水o個d人唔係咁，而且有排都未開檔。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">純粹提大家，如果今日想出身汗打波或者做觀眾反包圍，萬事小心，夠人先好<br />\n同埋影埋其他區o既大陸鄉里，表達好客之道，將佢地同連儂牆o既合照send去 <a href=\"http://12339.gov.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F12339.gov.cn&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8mt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=2e94259f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">12339.gov.cn</a>   同 hkleaks.ru 表揚佢地<